item.description:
The party we have all been waiting for!

Australia Day this year is on Sat Jan 24 at the Phoenix Landing at 2pm. Lots of Meat Pies, Aussie beer, Aussie music, Aussie trivia, and lots and lots of Aussie party animals will be in attendance as well! The infamous handball competition is back as well as the raffle of an Aussie hamper and good old fashioned meat tray.

$10 only for entry, dress Aussie, show your colors and get in early as it could pack out, last year was standing room only and this year is expected to be the same.

Bring it on!!!
